# Local GitHub Actions runner mapping (nektos/act).
# Apple Silicon Mac + OrbStack: linux/arm64 matches the host and avoids QEMU slowdowns.
# Intel Mac / GitHub ubuntu-latest parity / Linux x86_64 dev machines:
#   use --container-architecture linux/amd64 instead.
--container-architecture linux/arm64
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest
